INSYALL: wwwflypaper - Web page poison for email harvesters
-----------------------------------------------------------

The program is installed without the Perl .pl suffix. To
install in /usr/local

   make install

To install for private use

   make DESTDIR=$HOME prefix=/usr/local install

To make an install package:

   make DESTDIR=tmp exec_prefix=/usr man_prefix=/usr/share install
   (cd tmp/ && tar -jcvf package.tar.bz2 usr)

End of file
